{"name":"Mathlib.Tactic.Lint.Frontend","instances":[{"typeNames":["Mathlib.Tactic.Lint.LintVerbosity"],"name":"Mathlib.Tactic.Lint.instInhabitedLintVerbosity","className":"Inhabited"},{"typeNames":["Eq","Mathlib.Tactic.Lint.LintVerbosity"],"name":"Mathlib.Tactic.Lint.instDecidableEqLintVerbosity","className":"Decidable"},{"typeNames":["Mathlib.Tactic.Lint.LintVerbosity"],"name":"Mathlib.Tactic.Lint.instReprLintVerbosity","className":"Repr"}],"imports":["Init","Mathlib.Tactic.Lint.Basic"],"declarations":[{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/876d9cc42ccbfea023752e40e6edb7279d9c6b5a/Mathlib/Tactic/Lint/Frontend.lean#L218-L219","name":"Mathlib.Tactic.Lint.«command#list_linters»","docLink":"./Mathlib/Tactic/Lint/Frontend.html#Mathlib.Tactic.Lint.«command#list_linters»","doc":"The command `#list_linters` prints a list of all available linters. "},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/876d9cc42ccbfea023752e40e6edb7279d9c6b5a/Mathlib/Tactic/Lint/Frontend.lean#L184-L189","name":"Mathlib.Tactic.Lint.«command#lintMathlibAll+-*Only_»","docLink":"./Mathlib/Tactic/Lint/Frontend.html#Mathlib.Tactic.Lint.«command#lintMathlibAll+-*Only_»","doc":"The command `#lint` runs the linters on the current file (by default). "},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/876d9cc42ccbfea023752e40e6edb7279d9c6b5a/Mathlib/Tactic/Lint/Frontend.lean#L175-L181","name":"Mathlib.Tactic.Lint.getDeclsInMathlib","docLink":"./Mathlib/Tactic/Lint/Frontend.html#Mathlib.Tactic.Lint.getDeclsInMathlib","doc":""},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/876d9cc42ccbfea023752e40e6edb7279d9c6b5a/Mathlib/Tactic/Lint/Frontend.lean#L171-L173","name":"Mathlib.Tactic.Lint.getAllDecls","docLink":"./Mathlib/Tactic/Lint/Frontend.html#Mathlib.Tactic.Lint.getAllDecls","doc":""},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/876d9cc42ccbfea023752e40e6edb7279d9c6b5a/Mathlib/Tactic/Lint/Frontend.lean#L168-L169","name":"Mathlib.Tactic.Lint.getDeclsInCurrModule","docLink":"./Mathlib/Tactic/Lint/Frontend.html#Mathlib.Tactic.Lint.getDeclsInCurrModule","doc":""},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/876d9cc42ccbfea023752e40e6edb7279d9c6b5a/Mathlib/Tactic/Lint/Frontend.lean#L138-L166","name":"Mathlib.Tactic.Lint.formatLinterResults","docLink":"./Mathlib/Tactic/Lint/Frontend.html#Mathlib.Tactic.Lint.formatLinterResults","doc":"Formats the linter results as Lean code with comments and `#print` commands.\n"},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/876d9cc42ccbfea023752e40e6edb7279d9c6b5a/Mathlib/Tactic/Lint/Frontend.lean#L124-L133","name":"Mathlib.Tactic.Lint.groupedByFilename","docLink":"./Mathlib/Tactic/Lint/Frontend.html#Mathlib.Tactic.Lint.groupedByFilename","doc":"Formats a map of linter warnings grouped by filename with `-- filename` comments.\nThe first `drop_fn_chars` characters are stripped from the filename.\n"},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/876d9cc42ccbfea023752e40e6edb7279d9c6b5a/Mathlib/Tactic/Lint/Frontend.lean#L116-L118","name":"Mathlib.Tactic.Lint.printWarnings","docLink":"./Mathlib/Tactic/Lint/Frontend.html#Mathlib.Tactic.Lint.printWarnings","doc":"Formats a map of linter warnings using `print_warning`, sorted by line number. "},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/876d9cc42ccbfea023752e40e6edb7279d9c6b5a/Mathlib/Tactic/Lint/Frontend.lean#L112-L113","name":"Mathlib.Tactic.Lint.printWarning","docLink":"./Mathlib/Tactic/Lint/Frontend.html#Mathlib.Tactic.Lint.printWarning","doc":"Formats a linter warning as `#check` command with comment. "},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/876d9cc42ccbfea023752e40e6edb7279d9c6b5a/Mathlib/Tactic/Lint/Frontend.lean#L104-L109","name":"Mathlib.Tactic.Lint.sortResults","docLink":"./Mathlib/Tactic/Lint/Frontend.html#Mathlib.Tactic.Lint.sortResults","doc":"Sorts a map with declaration keys as names by line number. "},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/876d9cc42ccbfea023752e40e6edb7279d9c6b5a/Mathlib/Tactic/Lint/Frontend.lean#L80-L101","name":"Mathlib.Tactic.Lint.lintCore","docLink":"./Mathlib/Tactic/Lint/Frontend.html#Mathlib.Tactic.Lint.lintCore","doc":""},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/876d9cc42ccbfea023752e40e6edb7279d9c6b5a/Mathlib/Tactic/Lint/Frontend.lean#L74-L78","name":"Mathlib.Tactic.Lint.getChecks","docLink":"./Mathlib/Tactic/Lint/Frontend.html#Mathlib.Tactic.Lint.getChecks","doc":"`getChecks slow extra use_only` produces a list of linters.\n`extras` is a list of names that should resolve to declarations with type `linter`.\nIf `useOnly` is true, it only uses the linters in `extra`.\nOtherwise, it uses all linters in the environment tagged with `@[linter]`.\nIf `slow` is false, it only uses the fast default tests. "},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/876d9cc42ccbfea023752e40e6edb7279d9c6b5a/Mathlib/Tactic/Lint/Frontend.lean#L67-L67","name":"Mathlib.Tactic.Lint.instReprLintVerbosity","docLink":"./Mathlib/Tactic/Lint/Frontend.html#Mathlib.Tactic.Lint.instReprLintVerbosity","doc":""},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/876d9cc42ccbfea023752e40e6edb7279d9c6b5a/Mathlib/Tactic/Lint/Frontend.lean#L67-L67","name":"Mathlib.Tactic.Lint.instDecidableEqLintVerbosity","docLink":"./Mathlib/Tactic/Lint/Frontend.html#Mathlib.Tactic.Lint.instDecidableEqLintVerbosity","doc":""},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/876d9cc42ccbfea023752e40e6edb7279d9c6b5a/Mathlib/Tactic/Lint/Frontend.lean#L67-L67","name":"Mathlib.Tactic.Lint.instInhabitedLintVerbosity","docLink":"./Mathlib/Tactic/Lint/Frontend.html#Mathlib.Tactic.Lint.instInhabitedLintVerbosity","doc":""},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/876d9cc42ccbfea023752e40e6edb7279d9c6b5a/Mathlib/Tactic/Lint/Frontend.lean#L66-L67","name":"Mathlib.Tactic.Lint.LintVerbosity","docLink":"./Mathlib/Tactic/Lint/Frontend.html#Mathlib.Tactic.Lint.LintVerbosity","doc":"Verbosity for the linter output.\n* `low`: only print failing checks, print nothing on success.\n* `medium`: only print failing checks, print confirmation on success.\n* `high`: print output of every check.\n"},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/876d9cc42ccbfea023752e40e6edb7279d9c6b5a/Mathlib/Tactic/Lint/Frontend.lean#L50-L55","name":"Lean.TagAttribute.getDecls","docLink":"./Mathlib/Tactic/Lint/Frontend.html#Lean.TagAttribute.getDecls","doc":""}]}